<i>[Unfair Treaty]</i>

119
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,310
They definitely wouldn’t disagree

120
00:06:18,610 --> 00:06:20,250
with two Grand Soul Land Masters.

121
00:06:26,110 --> 00:06:27,650
Senior Dugu Bo was here?

122
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:30,550
He came for you.

123
00:06:30,550 --> 00:06:31,950
It seemed urgent.

124
00:06:33,810 --> 00:06:35,710
He probably ran into some trouble

125
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:37,550
and left without staying for long.

126
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:43,750
What would make that Old Freak be in such a rush?

127
00:06:44,210 --> 00:06:45,180
Could it be...

128
