with a mixed poison.

132
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,880
The cause

133
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:57,510
was a type of spice in his food.

134
00:06:57,650 --> 00:06:59,350
In the palace,

135
00:06:59,350 --> 00:07:03,050
only Xue Qing He uses that spice.

136
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:07,280
The Ning family’s little girl
said that Little Freak is back!

137
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,250
Frander.

138
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:09,310
Is he here?

139
00:07:10,150 --> 00:07:11,010
Little Freak.

140
00:07:11,010 --> 00:07:12,580
Emperor Xue Ye is about to die.

141
00:07:12,850 --> 00:07:13,450
What?

142
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:14,310
Old Freak.

143
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:16,050
Didn’t you tell me last time

144
00:07:16,050 --> 00:07:17,180
