145
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,450
was under control?

146
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,910
I did have it under control then.

147
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,780
But who would’ve thought

148
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:23,910
that he would become

149
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:25,050
suddenly poisoned again,

150
00:07:25,050 --> 00:07:27,580
and the situation is even worse this time.

151
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,550
What antidote did you use?

152
