I used Jade Phosphor Serpent King Venom,

153
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:34,110
attacking his poison with more poison

154
00:07:34,610 --> 00:07:36,110
to neutralize the mixed poison.

155
00:07:36,650 --> 00:07:38,780
I then used medicine to nurse his health.

156
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:40,210
But every time I neutralized it,

157
00:07:40,210 --> 00:07:42,310
