161
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:53,610
How many times have you neutralized it already?

162
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,610
Six.

163
00:07:55,610 --> 00:07:58,350
The time between each relapse
is also getting shorter.

164
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:00,050
If Emperor Xue Ye

165
00:08:00,050 --> 00:08:01,410
is not poisoned with a simple mixed poison,

166
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:03,010
but a more complicated one,

167
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:04,410
