171
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:14,750
Wait.

172
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,010
We need to find someone first

173
00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:17,010
and take him along.

174
00:08:17,010 --> 00:08:17,710
What?

175
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:19,910
You know someone else that’s good at using poison?

176
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,450
Let’s go.

177
00:08:22,450 --> 00:08:23,250
I’ll tell you on the way.

178
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:24,310
Teacher.

179
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:24,810
Dean.

180
00:08:24,810 --> 00:08:25,880
We’ll leave first.

181
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,710
Fatty.

182
00:08:26,710 --> 00:08:27,480
You stay here

183
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,550
