187
00:08:53,610 --> 00:08:56,450
All of the symptoms you described

188
00:08:56,450 --> 00:08:58,980
are signs of multiple mixed poisons.

189
00:08:59,610 --> 00:09:01,880
If we can’t find the root of the cause,

190
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,650
