191
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:07,880
<i>It seems like this person’s knowledge of poison</i>

192
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,880
<i>is no less than mine.</i>

193
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:12,280
Can you make an antidote?

194
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:14,880
As long as we can find the root of the poison,

195
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:17,110
I am fairly confident.

196
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,680
That’s great.

197
