214
00:11:52,935 --> 00:11:54,635
<i>about the royal soul masters being redeployed.</i>

215
00:11:54,635 --> 00:11:56,365
<i>The entire palace</i>

216
00:11:56,535 --> 00:11:58,465
<i>must be locked down by Xue Qing He.</i>

217
00:12:58,735 --> 00:13:00,665
<i>Old Freak is so frightened.</i>

218
00:13:00,665 --> 00:13:02,665
<i>These two people must have a higher level</i>

219
00:13:02,665 --> 00:13:04,265
<i>of soul power than him.</i>

220
00:13:04,265 --> 00:13:06,835
It turns out Tang Yin is Tang San.

221
00:13:07,235 --> 00:13:08,835
I made a mistake

222
00:13:08,835 --> 00:13:10,435
when we were in the Moon Pavilion.

223
00:13:12,835 --> 00:13:14,365
Brother Tang San.

224
00:13:14,795 --> 00:13:17,465
Why didn’t let them tell me you were here?

225
00:13:18,335 --> 00:13:20,235
