226
00:13:20,235 --> 00:13:22,095
Xue Ke keeps talking about you.

227
00:13:22,935 --> 00:13:25,065
Greetings, Crown Prince.

228
00:13:30,795 --> 00:13:32,095
Crown Prince.

229
00:13:32,095 --> 00:13:32,865
Greetings.

230
00:13:37,765 --> 00:13:39,195
Thank you for your kindness,

231
00:13:39,195 --> 00:13:40,535
Crown Prince.

232
00:13:41,095 --> 00:13:42,235
I was invited

233
00:13:42,235 --> 00:13:43,695
by Senior Dugu Bo

234
00:13:43,695 --> 00:13:45,065
to treat His Majesty.

235
00:13:45,065 --> 00:13:46,835
Will you let us in first

236
00:13:46,835 --> 00:13:48,065
to treat His Majesty?

237
00:13:48,365 --> 00:13:50,665
No need to worry about my father, brother.

238
00:13:50,665 --> 00:13:52,665
It’s not easy for you to come to the palace.

239
00:13:53,135 --> 00:13:54,665
Let me treat you to a meal

240
00:13:54,665 --> 00:13:56,665
and we can have a chat.

241
00:13:57,235 --> 00:13:58,265
It seems like

242
00:13:58,265 --> 00:13:59,635
all the guards here

243
00:13:59,635 --> 00:14:01,895
are from the Martial Soul Hall.

244
00:14:02,195 --> 00:14:03,835
Right, Crown Prince?

245
00:14:04,735 --> 00:14:05,765
Tang San.

246
00:14:05,765 --> 00:14:07,335
What nonsense is that?

247
00:14:07,765 --> 00:14:10,835
This is the Tian Dou Empire Palace.

248
00:14:11,265 --> 00:14:12,835
