251
00:14:16,035 --> 00:14:17,235
The two people next to you

252
00:14:17,235 --> 00:14:18,665
must be Grand Soul Land Masters, right?

253
00:14:18,665 --> 00:14:20,665
Why aren’t they with Emperor Xue Ye, protecting him,

254
00:14:20,665 --> 00:14:22,135
but with you instead?

255
00:14:22,365 --> 00:14:23,665
Besides, there are only a limited number

256
00:14:23,665 --> 00:14:25,435
of Grand Masters in the entire continent.

257
00:14:25,435 --> 00:14:26,695
Besides the Martial Soul Hall,

258
00:14:26,695 --> 00:14:28,295
who has this kind of power?

259
00:14:28,465 --> 00:14:29,595
Second,

260
00:14:30,395 --> 00:14:31,865
did you really replace all the royal guards

261
00:14:31,865 --> 00:14:33,565
with soul masters

262
00:14:33,835 --> 00:14:35,765
just to protect His Majesty?

263
00:14:36,665 --> 00:14:38,765
