264
00:14:39,035 --> 00:14:40,595
who is also my teacher?

265
00:14:41,135 --> 00:14:42,065
Third,

266
00:14:42,465 --> 00:14:45,235
you knew my real identity as soon as you saw me.

267
00:14:45,495 --> 00:14:46,965
But you didn’t question

268
00:14:46,965 --> 00:14:48,595
the medal I had at all.

269
00:14:49,265 --> 00:14:50,595
I’m positive that you are close

270
00:14:50,895 --> 00:14:53,165
with the Martial Soul Hall.

271
00:14:53,735 --> 00:14:56,735
